name: Madrepora Magna
description:
--Fig09--
Madrepora Magna is a magic being from another universe, so it cannot be classified within biology terms. ‘Where’ it comes from, there isn't time and space like we know, and there are at least 15 types of lightning, not only ‘light/dark’ like here.
They say Madrepora lives in the after after-death, or in the ‘second death place’, where people go not after body death, but after spirit death. Its mission given by God was to take care of those who abuse too much of their free will, and even break the eternal laws of this universe, and there with Madrepora they stay much more than trillions of eternities, purifying their soul with this mysterious and powerful being.
